quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Ta-seen tilka ayatualqur-ani wakitabin mubeen"
  27,2,"Hudan wabushra lilmu/mineen"
  27,3,"Allatheena yuqeemoona assalatawayu/toona azzakata wahum bil-akhiratihum yooqinoon"
  27,4,"Inna allatheena la yu/minoonabil-akhirati zayyanna lahum aAAmalahumfahum yaAAmahoon"
  27,5,"Ola-ika allatheena lahum soo-oalAAathabi wahum fee al-akhirati humu al-akhsaroon"
  27,6,"Wa-innaka latulaqqa alqur-anamin ladun hakeemin AAaleem"
  27,7,"Ith qala moosa li-ahlihiinnee anastu naran saateekum minhabikhabarin aw ateekum bishihabin qabasinlaAAallakum tastaloon"
  27,8,"Falamma jaaha noodiya anboorika man fee annari waman hawlahawasubhana Allahi rabbi alAAalameen"
  27,9,"Ya moosa innahu ana AllahualAAazeezu alhakeem"
  27,10,"Waalqi AAasaka falamma raahatahtazzu kaannaha jannun walla mudbiranwalam yuAAaqqib ya moosa la takhaf innee layakhafu ladayya almursaloon"
  27,11,"Illa man thalama thummabaddala husnan baAAda soo-in fa-innee ghafoorun raheem"
  27,12,"Waadkhil yadaka fee jaybika takhruj baydaamin ghayri soo-in fee tisAAi ayatin ilafirAAawna waqawmihi innahum kanoo qawman fasiqeen"
  27,13,"Falamma jaat-hum ayatunamubsiratan qaloo hatha sihrun mubeen"
